OL,4,G1630FVintage Antiques Roadshow
OL,5,     GMichael Aspel and a team of
OL,6,     Gexperts examine artefacts offered
OL,7,     Gup by the public at Knebworth
OL,8,     GHouse. Items featured include a
OL,9,     Gmarine chronometer and a diamond
OL,10,     Gbrooch.
OL,11,G1715FFlog It!
OL,12,     GPaul Martin is at Aberystwyth's
OL,13,     GOld College, the original site of
OL,14,     Gthe first university in Wales. He
OL,15,     Galso visits Laugharne, the home
OL,16,     Gof his literary hero Dylan Thomas.
OL,17,G1800FRichard Osman's House of Games
OL,18,     GAmy Gledhill, Jacqui Joseph,
OL,19,     GLaurence Llewelyn-Bowen and Tim
OL,20,     GVine test their trivia.
